Dynamite Abalone: Wabibi~! So you were hiding here, you
losers!! Bringing back two escaped bounties will surely
please Mayor Orca Broccoli!

Bunny-chan: Gyaah, Dynamite Abalone!? You... you sided with
the mayor...?

Cerberus Octopus: Eeek... Eeeeek!! The strongest monster in
the city is now the mayor's underling...!? This is
impossible... it's all over...

Originally, "The Moist Powder Magazine" Dynamite Abalone was
supposed to be Memimi's final monster fight opponent.
Despite being one-hit KO'd by Mayor Orca, no one doubts his
strength as he now serves under him...
